015 & 2020) to now. 

**Q1: Can you point me to examples of papers that were significant version updates, not introduction papers?** 
I found a previous issue discussion (e.g., https://github.com/openjournals/joss/issues/1162), but I wonder if you have any specific examples of papers that were significant version updates, not original papers?  I am hoping example papers might help us figure out how to handle nuanced but impactful updates where the change is essential, but the foundational information we are including may feel _known_ (or previously published). When does repeating things conceptually and omitting them in other places make sense or not? As software becomes more complex, this becomes more difficult without ignoring word count limits. ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/openjournals/joss/issues/1403/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/openjournals/joss/issues/1403/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/openjournals/joss/issues/comments/2565651036","html_url":"https://github.com/openjournals/joss/issues/1403#issuecomment-2565651036","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/openjournals/joss/issues/1403","id":2565651036,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAv-6eM6Y7Lpc","user":{"login":"EwoutH","id":15776622,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1Nzc2NjIy","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/15776622?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH","html_url":"https://github.com/EwoutH","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/EwoutH/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/u